Global Traffic Passenger Security Equipment Market Insights
Traffic Passenger Security Equipment Market size was valued at USD 5.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 10.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Traffic Passenger Security Equipment Market Overview
The global traffic passenger security equipment market is poised for significant growth, with a market value estimated at USD 20 billion in 2024. This market includes advanced safety and security solutions such as surveillance systems, biometric scanners, automated security checks, and more, which are becoming increasingly crucial for both public transportation systems and private sectors. The growing need for enhanced security and safety measures due to rising threats, along with the implementation of government regulations, is expected to drive the market's expansion. The increasing adoption of AI and IoT technologies for real-time monitoring and tracking further supports this growth trajectory.

